Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.17,0:01:19.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been a comedy duo for such a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.92,0:01:22.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can suddenly see you as my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:23.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.49,0:01:29.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi Risa, heartbroken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.25,0:01:39.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.39,0:01:43.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.12,0:01:45.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:48.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my name's Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.07,0:01:53.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.93,0:01:55.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:07.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If we'd met as a normal short girl and tall guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.09,0:02:08.93,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Look. See that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:10.44,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.74,0:02:10.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have ended up a comedy duo, and we'd naturally fall for one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.84,0:02:16.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd confess, and things might have gone well for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But the reality is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.53,0:02:25.50,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1028,1022)\3c&H0A0909&\q2\pos(375,395)}Back from the Dead!! Aim for Girlfriend Status!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.28,0:02:30.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...He's short.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:32.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts! That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:35.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:35.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.86,0:02:37.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa is so shocked you can see the whites of her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:42.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.94,0:02:45.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"W-What am I going to do"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Koizumi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:53.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you the one who told me to tell her what I was thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.30,0:02:54.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:02:56.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You're cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what don't you like about Risa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you, it's not that I don't like her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:03.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:06.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:09.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say for example I told you that these pickled radishes are now crabs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:14.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you really think, "Yes, that's true"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.85,0:03:15.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pickles... Pickles... Pickles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.86,0:03:16.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Crabs... Crabs... Crabs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:19.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:21.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say things we can't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.22,0:03:23.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oww! Oww! Don't! It was just an example!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't compare Risa with pickled radishes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.32,0:03:29.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:31.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too. Let's go play cards in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.78,0:03:34.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.79,0:03:37.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.85,0:03:38.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:42.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:43.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan, hold on, hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.58,0:03:49.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He just asked me to give them some time alone together during free time the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:53.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If we leave them alone right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:55.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...that would be bad, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.40,0:03:58.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry", "sorry"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times are you going to deal that finishing blow?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:07.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying "sorry" once is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:08.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:12.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It just makes me realize that this wasn't worth the effort at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:17.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I am just a pickled radish, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:20.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't become a crab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:22.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I know I picked a bad example, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:23.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You heard all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, at least you seem more lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"Lively"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I be lively?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:33.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:35.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So no matter what I say, it's just gonna upset you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:36.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.25,0:04:38.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.80,0:04:41.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just pretend that nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never speak of it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.07,0:04:49.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's fine by me if that's what you want, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:50.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.40,0:04:52.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So... is this how you treat guys you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:05.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh- Wh- What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.20,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a sense of delicacy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:09.64,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you can even say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.79,0:05:07.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Looks like they're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:09.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like they're back to their old selves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.94,0:05:14.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if they'll  just go back to being the way they were before...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's chat some more after I take my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:21.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:26.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I seem back to my old self just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A partner in our comedy duo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:30.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:33.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:34.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:39.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the boys in class 5 just confessed to Hikari-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.49,0:05:43.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Was it that guy she's liked all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah? So it was mutual then?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.03,0:05:49.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I haven't told anyone yet, but the truth is, I also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:53.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You spent the whole day together, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:56.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him that I like him, and the he said {\i1}"okay"{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.51,0:05:58.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.10,0:05:59.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:02.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh- What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone else is having a great time on this trip...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.68,0:06:09.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...yet here I am at rock bottom after being rejected on the very first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:15.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:17.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:21.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:27.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get this - I'm super popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls keep confessing to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's Ishida from class 4, and then from class 2 there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:34.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.67,0:06:36.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No boys allowed on this floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:37.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:38.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:40.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You lookin' for a fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to be so aggressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:43.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:46.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Haruka-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.90,0:06:49.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we have a picture taken together tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:55.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.08,0:06:58.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no need to hold back.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.50,0:07:02.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel like crying, then go ahead and cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:14.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. Let's go back to our room, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:16.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.47,0:07:22.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him to pretend that nothing happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.34,0:07:26.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but can I really do that to myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:29.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If none of this had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.25,0:07:31.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I didn't like Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.60,0:07:36.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.55,0:07:42.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:45.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to give up on Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:47.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a matter of giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pickled radishes can't become crabs, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:57.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still thinking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.59,0:08:01.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For starters, what are you going to do during free time the day after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:05.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to be with Otani-kun, you and I can go around together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:09.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:13.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd feel bad imposing on a lovey-dovey couple anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:19.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do, Risa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:21.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.65,0:08:24.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's not like I really mind being around with Otani that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:26.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:30.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who said I wanted us to go back to the way we were before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:34.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Avoiding him now would be pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.35,0:08:41.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:48.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who pushed you into confessing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:51.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like this is all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:57.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.56,0:09:02.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The confession... it was just me telling him how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:03.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.63,0:09:08.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm grateful that you motivated me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:09.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.69,0:09:12.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:14.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.17,0:09:18.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't touch me there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:22.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's making all those weird noises?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:22.45,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.90,0:09:24.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you guys woke us all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to play something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.30,0:09:28.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:29.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a pillow fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.52,0:09:33.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:37.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No good, no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:40.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm depressed, I'll worry everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.48,0:09:42.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:46.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just pretend that nothing happened, and go back to being the way I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point on brooding over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:56.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make the most out of this class trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:02.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:06.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, darling. Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.06,0:10:09.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How long are you going to be sleepy, shorty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:14.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a move on or you'll be left behind again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:19.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.34,0:10:23.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't want to go on feeling awkward forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.85,0:10:29.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just pretend nothing happened and go back to being part of our comedy duo again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:31.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.83,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get some snacks for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:37.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get these.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:43.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani! Otani!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.58,0:10:46.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this! Umibouzu's in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:49.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, he really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.61,0:10:51.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a local magazine you can only get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:56.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"After his concert on Sapporo, he left for Hakodate for a quick vacation"...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hakodate? Aren't we going there tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll have free time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:05.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try the soft serve ice cream he recommends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.55,0:11:08.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to have a picture taken in that exact same spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:11.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go there tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.96,0:11:13.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.85,0:11:16.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...if you're okay with being with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.47,0:11:20.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stop worrying about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:21.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:24.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm trying not to let it get to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.40,0:11:31.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:33.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better have brought a camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just take photos with our cell phones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:40.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:41.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:43.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we don't have to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.82,0:11:52.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Free time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.70,0:11:55.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we go first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:56.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The morning markets, the morning markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:59.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go eat the seafood Umibouzu recommends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:02.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Didn't you just eat breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,For someone so small, you sure eat a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.64,0:12:07.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Fine then, I'll just go by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.67,0:12:11.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:14.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to go halves with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:17.18,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:24.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.25,0:12:27.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.61,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Trams are awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:33.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. it really is shaped like a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Hurry up, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:41.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Rickshaws are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:46.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and take it. This is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. I'll pose normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.29,0:12:58.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget why we came to this specific spot in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:02.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember, it's your turn next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:14.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do still like Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:20.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But... if I tell him I like him, it'll get awkward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:23.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If we can stay like this forever, it's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:28.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:32.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you take a picture for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:34.40,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:36.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay, I'll take one for ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.38,0:13:37.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hehe, he said "'kay".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:40.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.78,0:13:41.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:44.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you from the Kansai district?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:45.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:47.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say {\i1}"You're kiddin' me"{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:49.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kiddin' me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.25,0:13:51.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's a real Kansai accent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:54.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:56.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there's something over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.45,0:14:03.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.27,0:14:05.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy sure was cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:07.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But who was that tall girl? His girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.93,0:14:09.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:16.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. No matter who's looking, no one would ever see me as his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:20.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.94,0:14:23.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn for a picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The magazine showed this spot too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can suddenly see you as my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.81,0:14:35.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what he means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.08,0:14:40.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can't think of me as a girlfriend, it's pointless to go on liking him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.09,0:14:43.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.85,0:14:46.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, a picture, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:48.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes please! It's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:55.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pretend nothing happened, and give up completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.14,0:14:59.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we head back to the meeting point soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.89,0:15:00.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:02.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My wallet.... I've lost it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:09.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:13.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's red, and round, with a picture of a rabbit on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you lose it when we took that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.45,0:15:16.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:41.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it hasn't been handed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.06,0:15:47.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go look around the places we went to today again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:50.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.08,0:15:52.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We wont find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.10,0:15:57.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There was only about 1,000 yen in it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:15:58.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,1,000 yen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:00.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much you could buy with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.06,0:16:02.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be cursed for giving it up, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's already time to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:10.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're late together again, more rumors will start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.63,0:16:13.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let them say whatever they want!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got time to spout such pointless crap, you've got time to keep looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:23.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.38,0:16:27.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I'll take this side of the road, and you take that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:32.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh- What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,D- Do you like that wallet that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:36.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.29,0:16:39.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I an idiot? I'm trying to help you-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.86,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:49.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I'd finally decided to give up for good...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:51.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:52.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...when you're so nice to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:00.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.18,0:17:02.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:02.33,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,U...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.34,0:17:04.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,"U"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.51,0:17:09.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,U...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.06,0:17:10.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,U...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a nice guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.97,0:17:28.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.44,0:17:31.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,G- G- G- G- Go say something to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:32.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,M- Me? Me?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:35.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell yes! This is a once in a lifetime opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, is this yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.51,0:17:46.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to turn it in at the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, of course. Sorry. I have 20-20 vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.38,0:17:52.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you on a class trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:53.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:56.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! It's past the time we were supposed to meet up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:57.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you like, we can drop you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.14,0:18:06.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to get a taxi to take us to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:06.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.95,0:18:10.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bouzu! I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:12.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up with the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.45,0:18:15.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, haven't I told you to call me {\i1}"Papa"{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:17.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibouzu's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.08,0:18:19.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibouzu's kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's married...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:25.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey boy, come help me hail a taxi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:26.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.03,0:18:27.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.69,0:18:28.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.60,0:18:31.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Gee, you sure are short.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.45,0:18:33.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But will there even be any taxis around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:35.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We already called ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.32,0:18:37.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you on a family vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:41.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He always says how much he likes it here, so we come here regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:45.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He may look scary, but he's a really gentle guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.75,0:18:50.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.91,0:18:52.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the same high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've been going out since back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't go out until long after we graduated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:04.27,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:11.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He confessed to me when we were in high school, but I rejected him in a big way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:18.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd been friends for ages, so I couldn't imagine dating him or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:20.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:23.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The taxi's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.33,0:19:25.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:27.36,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're married, and we even have a son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is really hard to predict, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:42.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So even pickled radishes can become crabs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:44.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.44,0:19:45.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:47.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:49.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:55.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I didn't fall for Otani right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.64,0:20:01.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani's reply may be {\i1}"sorry"{\i0} right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.81,0:20:06.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but if we take things slowly, bit by bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:11.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,...his answer might change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.86,0:20:18.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:23.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to force myself to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:31.06,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I got to meet Umibouzu. I'm so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.50,0:20:34.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:44.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to have to take back that "Let's pretend nothing happened".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.00,0:20:48.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I still like you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.45,0:20:50.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:02.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:08.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of dopey response is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.00,0:21:11.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you get for saying things like that out of the blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:15.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to, since you're always slow on the uptake. Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:17.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the slow one?
