Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:24.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tha...That's that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.32,0:21:27.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:31.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you on about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.35,0:21:31.96,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I'll make you regret saying "sorry",
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:37.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I like who I like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.13,0:21:40.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:23.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani-kun, are you doing anything for Christmas?
